      <section id="header-end" class="about-article">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; flex-basis: content; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;">
        </div>
        <article class="aboutpage">
          <h2>About Us</h2>
          <h3 style="font-style: italic;">We are passionate about developing websites and web apps that communicate to
            the world what makes you unique.</h3>
          <hr>
          <p>GoLive WebDev is run by a mother and son team, Michele and Anthony, both with unique skills. Michele
            started learning how to build web pages as a personal hobby. Through that, she found her employer needed
            that type of skill along with marketing skills to start email marketing campaigns. As a single parent, she
            was able to do this work from her home office, thus being a full time mom and provider.</p>
          <p>Anthony, took an interest in programming by watching his mom work. She encouraged his interest at a very
            young age &amp; she taught him some very basic HTML and signed him up for some computer
            courses for very young children. He took that interest and actively looked for more languages to learn. </p>
          <p>Now, they actively share their passion for coding together, having long discussions about different
            programming concepts &amp; best practices.</p>
          <p>When they found they were in need of a product or service, the first place they would look
            would be online. It amazed them both that so many businesses had no online presense or a poorly created
            website. Thus they created GoLive WebDev, a company focused on helping businesses brand themselves with a
            unique website, giving those businesses the power to be found.</p>
        </article>
